value.title: StarCraft 2: REYNOR PLAYING PROTOSS?! (Bly vs Reynor)
value.excerpt: Since there are not a lot of big offline tournaments on the horizon, a few SC2 pro gamers have decided to rank up their offraces over the last week or two in StarCraft 2.
